active_skill.name: Pull-Tab Bomb
active_skill.description:
Throws a bomb at the target, dealing Fire DMG and accumulating Fire Anomaly Buildup.

DMG Multiplier: 420%/448%/476%/504%/532%

Daze Multiplier: 246%/262.4%/278.8%/295.2%/311.6%

additional_ability.name: Building Heat
additional_ability.description: When there are 2 or more Fire Attribute characters in your squad: Bangboo Chain Attack inflicts 60%/75%/90%/105%/120% more Anomaly Buildup.

chain_attack.name: Shocking Gift
chain_attack.description:
Throws a bomb at the target, dealing Fire DMG and inflicting massive Fire Anomaly Buildup.

DMG Multiplier: 1041%/1110.4%/1179.8%/1249.2%/1318.6%

Daze Multiplier: 148.5%/158.4%/168.3%/178.2%/188.1%
